ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2013-14
PrecisAppointment of MARK BAILEY as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Austria, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador and Permanent Representative to the International Organizations, in Vienna; SHAWN BARBER as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Malawi, with residence in Maputo; PHILIPPE BAULNE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Guinea, with residence in Dakar; and CHRISTOPHER THORNLEY as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Ghana and as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Togolese Republic, with residence in Accra.
